			<h2 class="excerpt">时常感觉在演末日恐怖片。</h2>
		<div class="detail">
				<p>
	<strong>1. 宅。（看片/书/综艺量显著增加。）</strong> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<strong></strong><img src="http://cms.qdaily.com/uploads/image/201601/24603c0cc0af.jpg" width="550" height="413" title="2" alt="2" style="text-align:center;" /><strong></strong> 
</p>
<p>
	<strong>2. 宅的各种副作用。长胖。睡太多。效率低下。</strong> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<strong></strong> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/e5b1fe7ac37f.gif" width="498" height="280" title="2" alt="2" /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<strong>3. 头痛。眼睛痛。嗓子痛。心痛。</strong> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/e4b87ab56445.gif" width="500" height="382" title="2" alt="2" /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<strong>4. 更爱到家 app。</strong> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<strong></strong><img src="http://cms.qdaily.com/uploads/image/201601/9b3452a85ecf.gif" width="500" height="336" title="2" alt="2" style="text-align:center;" /><strong></strong> 
</p>
<div>
</div>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<strong>5. 口罩永远放在购物车。</strong> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
